{"word":"πίνω","slug":"πίνω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b><el>πίνω</el></b> [<a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ cp.\">cp.</a> <el><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:πόμα\">πόμα</a></el> and <el><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:πότος\">πότος</a></el>] ‘take in a liquid’, <b>drink<p class=\"pp3\"/>—<pp>a.</pp></b> in physical sense, usually of water or wine <b><a href='B:470 6:25'>Mt 6:25</a>; <a href='B:470 11:18'>11:18f</a>; <a href='B:470 26:29'>26:29</a>; <a href='B:470 27:34'>27:34</a>; <a href='B:480 16:18'>Mk 16:18</a>; <a href='B:490 1:15'>Lk 1:15</a>; <a href='B:490 12:19'>12:19</a>; <a href='B:490 13:26'>13:26</a>; <a href='B:500 4:7'>J 4:7</a>; <a href='B:510 9:9'>Ac 9:9</a>; <a href='B:510 23:12'>23:12</a>; <a href='B:520 14:21'>Ro 14:21</a>; <a href='B:530 9:4'>1 Cor 9:4</a>; <a href='B:530 10:4'>10:4</a>, <a href='B:530 10:7'>7</a>, <a href='B:530 10:21'>21</a>, <a href='B:530 10:31'>31</a>; <a href='B:530 11:22'>11:22</a>, <a href='B:530 11:25'>25</a>; <a href='B:530 15:32'>15:32</a>; <a href='B:730 16:6'>Rv 16:6</a>.<p class=\"pp3\"/>—<pp>b.</pp></b> in <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ transf.\">transf.</a> sense <b><a href='B:470 20:22'>Mt 20:22f</a>; <a href='B:470 26:27'>26:27</a>; <a href='B:480 10:38'>Mk 10:38f</a>; <a href='B:500 4:14'>J 4:14</a>; <a href='B:500 6:53'>6:53f</a>, 56; <a href='B:500 7:37'>7:37</a>; <a href='B:650 6:7'>Hb 6:7</a>; <a href='B:730 14:10'>Rv 14:10</a>.</b> <center id=\"nav_bottom\"> <a id=\"left_arrow\" href=\"S:πίναξ\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> <a id=\"bottom_home\" href=\"S:#1.Table of Contents\">&emsp;&emsp;</a> <a id=\"right_arrow\" href=\"S:πιότης\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> </center> "}]}